Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I select 'Yes' radio button from 'Contrast enhanced' box on Page 03
And	I go to Page 07 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Pleural thickening' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Characterization' tab is enabled and automatically selected
And 'Differential diagnosis' tab is enabled

When I am on 'Characterization' tab
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
AAnd 'Size' input field is enabled
And '2nd plane' input field is enabled
And '3rd plane' input field is enabled
And 'Diffuse' radio button is enabled
And 'Focal' radio button is enabled

And 'Obtused angulation of costophrenic angle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Nodular configuration' checkbox is enabled
And 'Locoregional osteolysis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Calcification' checkbox is enabled

And 'None' radio button is enabled
And 'Mild' radio button is enabled
And 'Marked' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Focal' radio button
Then 'Apical' radio button is enabled
And 'Basal' radio button is enabled
And 'Anterior' checkbox is enabled
And 'Lateral' checkbox is enabled
And 'Posterior' checkbox is enabled
And 'Fissural' checkbox is enabled
And 'Mediastinal' checkbox is enabled 

When I select 'Mild' radio button
Then 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Marked' radio button
Then 'Homogeneous' radio button is enabled
And 'Heterogeneous' radio button is enabled
